These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: pepper, carrot
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: french, malaysian
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goat
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, prince
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
4. the french is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk       | mirinda    |
| Food           | carrot | pepper |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | thriller   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | french     |
| Pet           | goat       | ferret     |
| Cigar     | montecristo     | prince        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, february
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, begonia
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
2 different pets are kept: bird, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is the fan of pop##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Birthday      | march        | february   |
| Flower         | begonia | zinnia |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Pet           | rat        | bird    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

