2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, swisher
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Beverage      | coffee    | sprite      |
| Food          | asparagus | pomegranate |
| Hobby           | dancing     | traveling      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       |
| Pet           | snake     | ferret      |
| Cigar     | swisher   | havana         |

 